scene.message:
Queen: Your symbol of hope,{nl}
Saeko,{wait_fr:30} has been sacrificed,{nl}
along with Tomomi.{waitkey}{clearbox}I am the Persona that{nl}
dwelt within Tomomi{wait_fr:30}{nl}
the Night Queen.{waitkey}For this, I thank you.{waitkey}{clearbox}Free of my host Tomomi,{nl}
free of the vessel mask,{nl}
I'm finally free.{waitkey}{clearbox}The "Eternal Night" has come,{nl}
and now I shall be complete.{waitkey}{clearbox}In nothingness and despair,{nl}
in white and black, I'll{nl}
blanket this whole world.{waitkey}{nl}
Ahahahahahahaha{waitkey}{ret}

Night Queen: You fools.{waitkey}Behold with your own eyes{nl}
the coming of the{nl}
"Eternal Night."{waitkey}{clearbox}From this Ice Castle,{nl}
from the castle's peak,
